{"tid":2188560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳共機遭台灣擊落 空軍駁斥：假訊息","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:48:17.000Z","uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"feed7014f339486c42d52e58fef5db6f03a9facc","tid":2188560,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">網傳共機遭台灣擊落 空軍駁斥：假訊息</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/04 17:59<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者游凱翔台北4日電）網傳「台灣擊落一架中共SU-35戰機」，空軍司令部今天下午發布新聞稿，駁斥此為假訊息、子虛烏有，完全不是事實，並強烈譴責這種惡意行為。<br />\n<br />\n臉書粉絲團Defence Aviation Post下午發文表示，因一架中國蘇愷35（Su-35）戰機侵犯台灣海峽，遭台灣空軍擊落，中國飛行員則受傷且被逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n對此，空軍司令部發布新聞稿，駁斥此為假訊息、子虛烏有，完全不是事實。<br />\n<br />\n空軍強調，對於網路上有心人士刻意製造、傳播不實的假訊息，企圖混淆視聽，居心叵測，空軍強烈譴責這種惡意行為；空軍也表示，為維護領空安全，空軍對於台海周邊海、空域狀況，將持續採取嚴密監控作為，並適時提供正確資訊，防止偽假消息流傳，避免造成社會不安，籲請國人放心。（編輯：黃國倫）1090904<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009040249.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202009040249.aspx&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=d0144696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009040249.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n=================================================<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/118692031_1232168780478693_7655288871777959746_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=5IJKtz3bkb4AX87_5Ti&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-2.fna&amp;oh=2f5625d6b651f3ca4f3de14a8151d38b&amp;oe=5F75B485\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F118692031_1232168780478693_7655288871777959746_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3D5IJKtz3bkb4AX87_5Ti%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-2.fna%26oh%3D2f5625d6b651f3ca4f3de14a8151d38b%26oe%3D5F75B485&h=3d54e6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/defenceaviationpost1/photos/a.232357630459818/1232168777145360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdefenceaviationpost1%2Fphotos%2Fa.232357630459818%2F1232168777145360&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=cdea5648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/defenceaviationpost1/photos/a.232357630459818/1232168777145360</a>"},{"pid":"a45b8e796ff8df45835f53a5f9b18a2c9ecb8668","tid":2188560,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b7dc934f816730d8af9015e9e9fdc3e77230ff","tid":2188560,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:16:59.000Z","msg":"印度也急於想讓台灣加入抗共戰爭"},{"pid":"7adc24bc7e6a307cde1734a02da684b20bd482d8","tid":2188560,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Maverick_bharat/status/1301789461060022273?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMaverick_bharat%2Fstatus%2F1301789461060022273%3Fs%3D20&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=9680a11d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMaverick_bharat%2Fstatus%2F1301789461060022273%3Fs%3D20&h=0e633669\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Maverick_bharat/status/1301789461060022273?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片拍攝時間不詳，有推文聲稱拍攝地點是在廣西桂林，是否真的剛發生墜機，也暫時未能查證，但奇怪的是同一時間有多個推特帳號轉傳相關影片，並加註一段貼文：「台灣空軍擊落了飛越台灣海峽中線的解放軍蘇愷-35」，完全沒有附上任何證明。只有少數網友冷靜留言駁斥：「墜機地點是在廣西桂林，離台灣太遠了。」"},{"pid":"31d146ace45574e48d70359b4d449bd20ba6f1ee","tid":2188560,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"網傳共機遭台灣擊落 空軍駁斥：假訊息"},{"pid":"0e6095c77d50f1ed3bd8637e00b0ba5097fc1db8","tid":2188560,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"貢嘰"},{"pid":"06799ce97683f83569b3b6b6b409604a0b04b0fc","tid":2188560,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"推"}]}